    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Invitation for Commutation Service Tender</h1>
        </header>
        <section class="description">
            <p>We hereby invite interested and qualified parties to submit proposals for providing daily commuting services between Bahubazar (Source) and PHQ (Destination) in the morning at 9:30 AM and from PHQ (Source) to Bahubazar in the evening at 6:00 PM. The service provider is expected to ensure reliable, safe, and comfortable transportation for passengers throughout the specified routes.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="scope-of-work">
            <h2>Scope of Work</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Departure from Bahubazar to PHQ: 9:30 AM</li>
                <li>Departure from PHQ to Bahubazar: 6:00 PM</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section class="terms-conditions">
            <h2>Terms and Conditions</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>The service provider must possess valid permits and licenses for operating transportation services on the designated route.</li>
                <li>Vehicles used for transportation must be well-maintained, clean, and compliant with all safety regulations.</li>
                <li>The safety and security of passengers and their belongings during transit are the responsibility of the service provider.</li>
                <li>Any deviations from the specified schedule must be communicated and approved in advance by the contracting authority.</li>
                <li>The selected vendor will be compensated with a monthly payment of Rs. 500 for petrol expenses incurred during the provision of services.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section class="submission-requirements">
            <h2>Submission Requirements</h2>
            <p>Interested parties are requested to submit their proposals in sealed envelopes marked "Commutation Service Tender" to the address provided below no later than <strong>30th May at 6 PM</strong>.</p>
            <address>
                C/o-Abnish Kumar Singh<br>
                Data Center, Police Head Quarter, HEC, Dhurwa, Ranchi-834004
            </address>
            <p>The proposal should include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Company profile, highlighting relevant experience in providing transportation services.</li>
                <li>Details of the proposed vehicles, including registration documents and insurance.</li>
                <li>Proposed schedule and route plan.</li>
                <li>Cost breakdown, specifying the monthly rate for petrol expenses.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section class="selection-criteria">
            <h2>Selection Criteria</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Experience and track record in operating transportation services.</li>
                <li>Compliance with safety standards and regulations.</li>
                <li>Competitive pricing for the proposed services.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section class="important-dates">
            <h2>Important Dates</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Deadline for Submission: <strong>30th May at 6 PM</strong></li>
                <li>Evaluation Period: <strong>1 day</strong></li>
            </ul>
        </section>
